text: Decades Rock Live! is an American TV series of live concerts. The program premiered on VH1 Classic in the winter of 2006. Lineups included: * Heart with special guests Alice in Chains, Dave Navarro, Rufus Wainwright, Carrie Underwood, Gretchen Wilson, Duff McKagan and Phil Anselmo (March 10, 2006) ==References== Category:Rock festivals
title: Decades Rock Live!
